&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="1SOZ37"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"This case turns your Apple Watch into a tiny iPod","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200520/tinypod-apple-watch-accessory-ipod-case-scroll-wheel"},{"title":"How to preorder Samsung’s Galaxy Watch 7, Galaxy Watch Ultra, and the Galaxy Ring","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/10/24194952/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-ring-ultra-preorder-buy-price-availability-release-date"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="IhZxNH"&gt;For its price, the GTR 4 offers an impressive number of features. It does a good job of tracking all kinds of health and fitness metrics, from heart, sleep, and stress to your menstrual cycle, while boasting over 150 sport...&lt;/p&gt;
