      &lt;img alt="A person wearing the blue Shokz OpenRun Pro headphones on a running track." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/i5Qdg26iVltRtiP48X2mLu4xF1A=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73474773/shokz_openrun_pro_headphones.0.jpg" /&gt;
